OL,3,CM&S demands police are given
OL,4,C'resources they need' following
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FIt comes after teenagers arranged to
OL,8,Fmeet in the last week as part of "link-
OL,9,Fups", using social media apps
OL,10,Fincluding TikTok and Snapchat, before
OL,11,Fthey surged into shops, as
OL,12,FCorrespondent Katy Rickitt reports
OL,14,FThe boss of M&S has called for police
OL,15,Fto be given "the resources they need"
OL,16,Fto tackle crime on the high street,
OL,17,Fwhich he says has become "more brazen,
OL,18,Fmore organised and more aggressive".
OL,26,@pD@bOUqD@DO]yD@ZOUzD@cO]
