OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775250670
OL,3,CM&S demands police are given
OL,4,C'resources they need' following
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FRetail director Thinus Keeve called on
OL,8,Fthe government and City Hall in London
OL,9,Fto do more to tackle anti-social
OL,10,Fbehaviour following large groups of
OL,11,Fteenagers, encouraged by social media,
OL,12,Fswarming high streets.
OL,14,FIn a statement on the retail giant's
OL,15,Fwebsite, Mr Keeve said: "Without a
OL,16,Fgovernment seriously cracking down on
OL,17,Fcrime and a Mayor that prioritises
OL,18,Feffective policing we are powerless.
OL,26,@wD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
