OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775250670
OL,3,CM&S demands police are given
OL,4,C'resources they need' following
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,F"We need a stronger, faster and more
OL,8,Fconsistent police response, using
OL,9,Ftools that already exist to target
OL,10,Frepeat offenders and crime hotspots.
OL,12,F"It's a clear ask: support our police.
OL,13,FHelp them show up in our communities
OL,14,Fwhen and where we need them. Give them
OL,15,Fthe resources they need to tackle
OL,16,Fcrime effectively and ensure they work
OL,17,Fwith retailers to consistently use the
OL,18,Ftools we've developed to share data
OL,19,Fand help them actively target
OL,20,Foffenders," he added.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
