OL,3,CM&S demands police are given
OL,4,C'resources they need' following
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FIt comes after teenagers arranged to
OL,8,Fmeet in Clapham, south London, in the
OL,9,Flast week as part of "link-ups", using
OL,10,Fsocial media apps including TikTok and
OL,11,FSnapchat, before they surged into
OL,12,Fshops.
OL,14,FAround 100 officers responded to
OL,15,Fantisocial behaviour on Tuesday,
OL,16,Faccording to the Metropolitan Police.
OL,17,FFive people were assaulted, including
OL,18,Ffour police officers.
OL,26,@qD@VOUqD@_O]
