OL,3,CM&S demands police are given
OL,4,C'resources they need' following
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FOn Thursday, Greater Manchester Police
OL,8,F(GMP) said a 48-hour dispersal order
OL,9,Fis in place covering Rochdale town
OL,10,Fcentre until Saturday at 11.30am.
OL,12,FGroups of young people were reported
OL,13,Fto be harassing staff and causing
OL,14,Fcriminal damage at a business and in
OL,15,Fthe town centre on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
