OL,3,CM&S demands police are given
OL,4,C'resources they need' following
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FThe London mayor has condemned the
OL,8,Fscenes of teenagers in Clapham as
OL,9,F"utterly unacceptable" and said
OL,10,Ffurther arrests were likely within
OL,11,Fdays as officers review CCTV and
OL,12,Fbodyworn video.
OL,14,FHe warned "the culprits will face the
OL,15,Ffull force of the law" and said police
OL,16,Fare working with social media
OL,17,Fcompanies to try to clamp down on
OL,18,F"viral online content which promotes
OL,19,Fviolence and theft".
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@VO]vD@KOUwD@VO]zD@AOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
