OL,3,CM&S demands police are given
OL,4,C'resources they need' following
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,F"Not only did they spread fear in the
OL,8,Flocal community, but assaulting and
OL,9,Fintimidating hard-working retail staff
OL,10,Fand police officers are serious
OL,11,Foffences," Khan said.
OL,13,FThe Met are taking "a zero-tolerance
OL,14,Fapproach to any form of criminality",
OL,15,Fincreasing officer numbers in hotspot
OL,16,Fareas and potentially using dispersal
OL,17,Forders.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@JO]uD@TOUvD@dO]
