OL,3,CM&S demands police are given
OL,4,C'resources they need' following
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FInspector Meena Yasin, from the GMP's
OL,8,FRochdale district, said: "We have
OL,9,Fimplemented this order to provide
OL,10,Ffurther powers for officers in the
OL,11,Farea to robustly deal with anti-social
OL,12,Fbehaviour, and to protect people and
OL,13,Fbusinesses."
